you will need to install python dev utils 
or will get error
fatal error: Python.h

sudo apt-get install python2.6-dev

or whatever your version of python is
e.g. python -V to find out

install python twisted framework
http://twistedmatrix.com/
sudo apt-get install python-twisted

sudo cp service/fireshark.py /usr/sbin/
sudo cp service/firesharkprofilemanager.py /usr/sbin/
sudo cp service/firefoxprocess.py /usr/sbin/

sudo chmod 777 /usr/sbin/fire*

sudo cp daemon/fireshark /etc/init.d/

sudo chmod 777 /etc/init.d/fireshark

http://blog.martin-lyness.com/archives/installing-xvfb-on-ubuntu-9-10-karmic-koala
install xfonts-base!!!
sudo aptitude install x11-xkb-utils
sudo aptitude install xfonts-100dpi xfonts-75dpi xfonts-scalable xfonts-cyrillic
sudo aptitude install xserver-xorg-core
sudo aptitude remove dbus??? not sure about this one
